{"id": 1873, "genre": 1001, "title": "你所在的行业都是如何委婉地表达“no”的？", "description": "不要不行不可以，是行不通的，正确的拒绝姿势应该是这样婶儿的。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 3807, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170828110218W0ShZoObVDBxgA8m.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-31T03:00:06Z", "options": [{"id": 233984, "content": "面试官:有消息我们会通知你的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1115367}, {"id": 234497, "content": "石油工人:加大产量我们要跟领导汇报", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1127457}, {"id": 233730, "content": "我们尽力了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951024}, {"id": 233219, "content": "新媒体：这个还可以再优化一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 990697}, {"id": 233475, "content": "我们一定会好好考虑的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122213}, {"id": 233732, "content": "实习生：这个我问问我老大。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686315}, {"id": 233483, "content": "周老头，你个是个自私得人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122267}, {"id": 240652, "content": "我回去问下领导意见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080042}, {"id": 234511, "content": "医疗器械工程师：好的 但这个我需要和我们领导先沟通", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028127}, {"id": 251919, "content": "假设计：这个……价格很高的 而且时间会很久", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1199177}, {"id": 233744, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124142}, {"id": 232980, "content": "您写个情况说明找领导签个字吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115802}, {"id": 233748, "content": "教师：这个说法同学们同意吗?有没有更好的想法呢?大家说说看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922851}, {"id": 232981, "content": "lol玩家：不存在的！", "image": "img/option/option/20170831150623Olw9hU1RTa7F6tfq.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119506}, {"id": 232982, "content": "凌晨两点还在加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770560}, {"id": 232983, "content": "这个，我们要问一下总部的意见。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097506}, {"id": 232984, "content": "这个测试在上个版本测试是通过的。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1110356}, {"id": 233496, "content": "客户爸爸：这个我不能接受", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 779602}, {"id": 234776, "content": "我们需要再上一次会.", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136629}, {"id": 232985, "content": "有好多人字都打错了……“在考虑一下”应该是“再”。不是“报歉”是“抱歉”", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829863}, {"id": 233241, "content": "医生：你们家再考虑考虑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120913}, {"id": 232986, "content": "你一个好人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120586}, {"id": 233242, "content": "我这里权限最多给你打四折", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1117745}, {"id": 232988, "content": "学生：不想", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081628}, {"id": 232989, "content": "Me: Moorabbin Ground, Echo Oscar Kilo, request taxi to runway 35R\nMB Ground: Negative. Your company want you to go back. ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081308}, {"id": 232990, "content": "这个点数太低了，我们不赚钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253146}, {"id": 233502, "content": "无能为力啊，爱莫能助", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122368}, {"id": 232991, "content": "我看完会打电话给你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120606}, {"id": 233247, "content": "阿岳:我觉得很普通", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104397}, {"id": 233503, "content": "正在走流程，也许会一直走流程", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958420}, {"id": 233249, "content": "有需要会找你们的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879505}, {"id": 233761, "content": "呃，这个制度是这么规定的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124508}, {"id": 234785, "content": "公安局办公室:哦这个需要请示一下我们领导/这个不是我们在管", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129885}, {"id": 232994, "content": "幼师：我们明天可以试试哦~", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120609}, {"id": 232996, "content": "没有领导认可，我这也不好办哇", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891784}, {"id": 232997, "content": "这个要再确认一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 856539}, {"id": 233509, "content": "你的孩子其实很聪明的，在努力点就肯定行！（总不能说没救了吧。。）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1083622}, {"id": 232998, "content": "设计专业的老师：难看，砍掉，重做", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930185}, {"id": 232999, "content": "看完和你再联系，谢谢！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065318}, {"id": 233001, "content": "朋友家做客:好的我下次一定来吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113860}, {"id": 233002, "content": "?", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810919}, {"id": 233003, "content": "有人找我借钱，    没钱可以借  这年头欠人钱的是大爷", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120350}, {"id": 233004, "content": "有空约", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1117969}, {"id": 233005, "content": "二手车：我可以给你看我们的账本（合同）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120664}, {"id": 234285, "content": "等后续通知哈～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1102338}, {"id": 233007, "content": "医学：这个我们还得再会诊研究一下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1115281}, {"id": 233008, "content": "什么？刚刚信号不好！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1117704}, {"id": 233009, "content": "我已经有男朋友了", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 874300}, {"id": 233010, "content": "我们是民主集中制，这事儿还需要上会讨论下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028568}, {"id": 234034, "content": "只有酒店狗 很难拒绝吧 但是 要做有原则的酒店狗 不能惯着坏习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735660}]}